25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：负责主机加固、基线核查和合规整改的安全或运维同学。\n阅读前提：具备 Linux / Windows 基础管理经验。\n核心收获：把基线要求拆成可执行的检查项、整改项和自动化核查思路。\n说明：不同发行版与系统版本的命令行为可能不同，落地前请先在测试环境验证。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"安全加固是将系统从默认的\"开箱即用\"状态调整为符合安全最佳实践的状态。许多安全事件的根本原因并非零日漏洞，而是系统配置不当——默认密码未修改、不必要的服务暴露、过于宽松的权限设置。CIS Benchmark（互联网安全中心基准）提供了一套业界公认的安全配置标准，本文将以此为核心，结合 Linux 和 Windows 的具体加固操作，以及 Lynis 和 OpenSCAP 等自动化工具，构建一份系统化的安全加固清单。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"安全基线概念","children":["安全基线概念",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#安全基线概念","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"安全基线（Security Baseline）是指一组经过验证的最低安全配置要求，用于确保系统在部署和运行过程中达到可接受的安全水平。"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"安全基线的核心价值："}]}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"标准化"}],"：为不同系统建立统一的安全配置标准，避免\"千人千面\"的配置差异"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"可度量"}],"：提供明确的检查项和预期值，使安全状态可以量化评估"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"可重复"}],"：基于脚本和工具实现自动化核查和配置，确保一致性"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"合规性"}],"：满足等保、ISO 27001、PCI DSS 等合规框架对安全配置的要求"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"安全基线的制定通常参考行业标准（如 CIS Benchmark）并结合组织自身的业务场景和风险偏好进行裁剪。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"cis-benchmark-详解","children":["CIS Benchmark 详解",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cis-benchmark-详解","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"CIS（Center for Internet Security）是一个全球性的非营利组织，其发布的 CIS Benchmark 覆盖了操作系统、数据库、云平台、网络设备、中间件等 100 多类 IT 产品的安全配置建议。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"评分机制","children":["评分机制",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#评分机制","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"CIS Benchmark 中的每一条配置建议都标注了评分状态（Scored/Not Scored）："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Scored（计分项）"}],"：不符合该项配置将导致基线评分下降，属于必须满足的安全要求"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Not Scored（非计分项）"}],"：属于建议性配置，不影响评分但有助于提升安全性"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"level-1-与-level-2","children":["Level 1 与 Level 2",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#level-1-与-level-2","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"级别"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"描述"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"适用场景"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Level 1"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"基础安全加固。实施后对系统功能和性能影响极小，适用于所有系统"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"所有生产环境必须满足"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Level 2"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"深度安全加固。可能影响系统便利性或性能，适用于高安全要求环境"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"金融、政务、涉密系统"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"cis-benchmark-文档获取","children":["CIS Benchmark 文档获取",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cis-benchmark-文档获取","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"linux-安全加固","children":["Linux 安全加固",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#linux-安全加固","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"ssh-加固","children":["SSH 加固",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#ssh-加固","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"SSH 是 Linux 服务器最常用的远程管理入口，也是暴力破解攻击的首要目标。"}],"\n","$L2e","\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"内核参数调优","children":["内核参数调优",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#内核参数调优","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"文件权限加固","children":["文件权限加固",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#文件权限加固","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"账户与密码策略","children":["账户与密码策略",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#账户与密码策略","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"windows-安全加固","children":["Windows 安全加固",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#windows-安全加固","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"组策略配置","children":["组策略配置",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#组策略配置","children":"$L33"}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n","$L35","\n","$L36","\n","$L37","\n","$L38","\n","$L39","\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50"]
