41:["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Hardening Index"}],"：系统加固指数，满分 100，越高越好。新装系统通常在 50-65 之间"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Warnings"}],"：红色警告项，应优先处理"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Suggestions"}],"：黄色建议项，逐项评估并实施"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Tests Performed"}],"：显示执行了多少项检测和跳过了多少项"]}],"\n"]}]
